    <pre class="bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto my-6"><code class="text-gray-300">=== Grid lookup: existence in discrete domain ===
  pigeonhole            kill: Same-size sets or need witness
                        escalate: probabilistic_method
  induction             kill: Residual loses structure
